36
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,830
Grandmother,

37
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,510
why did you keep your condition secret?

38
00:02:22,790 --> 00:02:24,480
Those senior officials

39
00:02:25,790 --> 00:02:27,350
wouldn’t dare touch the Bans

40
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,280
as long as I’m around.

41
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,880
But once they found out I’m sick,

42
00:02:33,350 --> 00:02:35,630
they’d sure come at us.

43
00:02:36,350 --> 00:02:37,200
Understand?

44
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:45,390
I’m confused about one thing.

45
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,830
You had helped Physician Zhang a lot.

46
00:02:48,390 --> 00:02:49,790
Why did he try to poison you?

47
00:02:51,390 --> 00:02:54,040
He’s timid by nature,

48
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,910
and must’ve acted under coercion.

49
00:02:56,950 --> 00:02:58,630
That’s not an excuse.

50
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,630
Hadn’t it been for Count Cheng’an,

51
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,440
there would’ve been dire consequences.

52
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,160
Hua,

53
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:08,320
that man is secretive.

54
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:11,630
You must watch out for him.

55
00:03:12,390 --> 00:03:15,110
Are you warning me

56
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,160
against someone who helped us?

57
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:22,630
Gentlemen put principles
before themselves,

58
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:25,510
while the snobs are the opposite.

59
00:03:26,110 --> 00:03:29,000
Physician Zhang meant
to protect himself,

60
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,600
but Count Cheng’an

61
00:03:32,830 --> 00:03:37,040
is a mystery even to me.

62
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:42,830
Grandmother, you’re worrying too much.

63
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:45,110
I can’t read his mind, either,

64
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:46,670
but I’m sure

65
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,910
he won’t harm us.

66
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,950
If one day,

67
00:03:49,510 --> 00:03:51,510
he dares to do that,

68
00:03:51,510 --> 00:03:52,280
I would

69
00:03:52,830 --> 00:03:55,040
beat him to a pulp.

70
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:02,910
When can you act like a lady?

71
00:04:13,350 --> 00:04:14,070
Madam.

72
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,760
Princess.

73
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:19,600
Grandmother said
Physician Zhang was under threat,

74
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,320
but by whom?

75
00:04:21,710 --> 00:04:23,200
Who would dare touch our people?

76
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,710
Prince Luo did it?

77
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:30,070
All that about
the Tiger Tally is a secret.

78
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:32,630
Few have access to it

79
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:35,070
other than His Majesty
and some senior officials.

80
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:38,030
Clearly, he was
plotting against Crown Prince.

81
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,440
The rest of us

82
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,560
were only his pawns.

83
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:46,390
Now that Her Highness is safe,

84
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:49,000
the mastermind

85
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,800
will pay the price eventually.

86
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:54,200
Don’t bother yourself with it.

87
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,800
Grandmother’s safety is at risk.

88
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,800
I must get to the bottom of it.

89
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,510
Your Grace, Your Grace,

90
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,800
I’ve tracked Physician Zhang down.

91
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,920
He’s hiding outside the city. Let’s go.

92
00:05:05,150 --> 00:05:05,800
-Let’s go.
-Let’s go.

93
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:08,760
Who is it?

94
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,800
It’s me, Princess.

95
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,680
I was about to bring Her Highness

96
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,630
freshly made desserts.

97
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,120
This is it, Your Grace.

98
00:05:23,710 --> 00:05:25,070
The open door

99
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,240
must be a sham.

100
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:27,590
I won’t take it.

101
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:28,950
Let’s go.

102
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,320
Count Cheng’an!

103
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,830
What are you doing here?

104
00:06:04,150 --> 00:06:05,950
I said I’d find out the truth for you.

105
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:08,830
Thank you.

106
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,560
Who’s the culprit?

107
00:06:11,590 --> 00:06:12,680
Don’t know yet.

108
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,030
Someone is there.

109
00:06:16,590 --> 00:06:17,320
I’ll take the back door.

110
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:17,950
You take the back door.

111
00:06:20,710 --> 00:06:21,360
Come.

112
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,000
Clear.

113
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,440
He’s gone.
You must seize him, Your Grace.

114
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,470
Relax.

115
00:06:50,470 --> 00:06:51,590
Count Cheng’an

116
00:06:51,590 --> 00:06:52,240
is waiting to catch him in the back.

117
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,510
We got company.

118
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,880
Go help Count Cheng’an.

119
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,920
I got this.

120
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,240
We cannot lose that physician again.

121
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:08,030
Bring it on.

122
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,200
Spare me, please!

123
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,680
Go, Young Master!

124
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,630
Let’s go!

125
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,440
I didn’t expect you’d save me, Count.

126
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,440
Physician Zhang,

127
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,630
why did Prince Luo
want Princess Royal dead?

128
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:00,710
What’s he up to?

129
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,120
Here’s the thing.

130
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,880
That day, I overheard him saying...

131
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:14,030
Silencing a witness!

132
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,470
Good to see you again, Count Cheng’an.

133
00:08:30,590 --> 00:08:31,710
Have you

134
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,390
considered my offer?

135
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:34,880
I never work with people

136
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,880
I don’t know.

137
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,470
You’re the wisest man in the country.

138
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:41,520
I gave you that letter

139
00:08:41,710 --> 00:08:43,200
for a reason.

140
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:45,560
I hope

141
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:47,200
you can enlighten me.

142
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,230
No one dares to

143
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,750
reopen the case of the Rongs’ deaths.

144
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,830
Prince Luo is your only hope

145
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,560
to get justice.

146
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:55,950
Don’t you agree?

147
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,920
He appreciates men of talent.

148
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,470
A fine fowl like you
should perch on a fine tree.

149
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:13,920
He...

150
00:09:15,950 --> 00:09:16,440
He...

151
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:17,990
Who killed him?

152
00:09:22,470 --> 00:09:23,280
Physician Zhang,

153
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:26,640
Luo...

154
00:09:27,830 --> 00:09:28,640
Luo...

155
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,870
Prince Luo, Jiang Luo!

156
00:09:39,990 --> 00:09:41,110
He did it.

157
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,400
Don’t jump to conclusions.

158
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,750
I should’ve known that

159
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,640
