160
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:47,990
Bastard!

161
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:49,920
How dare he!

162
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:52,280
Princess.

163
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:57,200
Thanks for your help. Good day.

164
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:04,870
Hua,

165
00:10:05,590 --> 00:10:06,950
who told you

166
00:10:06,950 --> 00:10:09,200
Prince Luo tried to
harm your grandmother?

167
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:12,200
