172
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:20,280
Because of him, Grandmother almost...

173
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,950
Anyway, he’s a pest.

174
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,110
Hua has a point.

175
00:10:30,470 --> 00:10:33,160
Did you... Dream about something else?

176
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,230
No.

177
00:10:35,070 --> 00:10:36,350
Think about it.

178
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,640
What he said and did

179
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:39,320
at the banquet

180
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,680
